</div>
        <div class=3D"method-desc">Attended trade shows, pop-ups, and vendo=
r events to observe consumer behavior firsthand and build sourcing relation=
ships. On-the-ground insights surfaced demand signals that quantitative dat=
a alone could not capture.</div>
      </div>
      <div class=3D"method-card">
        <div class=3D"method-icon">
          <svg viewBox=3D"0 0 36 36" fill=3D"none" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.o=
