        <div class=3D"method-desc">Applied economic indicators, CPI, inflat=
ion rate, real consumer spending, and crypto asset prices, to model demand =
trajectories across product categories. Correlated macro shifts with observ=
ed secondary market pricing to identify early signals.</div>
      </div>
