urcing decisions. Translated raw market observations into actionable recomm=
endations with results that could be tracked.</div>
      </div>
      <div class=3D"method-card" style=3D"grid-column:1/-1;">
        <div class=3D"method-icon">
          <svg viewBox=3D"0 0 36 36" fill=3D"none" xmlns=3D"http://www.w3.o=
