        <div class=3D"method-desc">Applied working knowledge of retail back=
end systems, request routing, and inventory endpoint behavior to monitor st=
ock availability at scale. Configured proxy and ISP networks to distribute =
monitoring across retailer infrastructure, enabling real-time visibility in=
to restock events across multiple channels at the same timely.</div>
      </div>
